Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七话 冷若寒风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.99,0:02:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校停课了 但令千金的同学还没回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.41,0:02:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家双胞胎的另一个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天起也没回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们猜测是不是被卷入什么事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 令千金平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过请您转告她 最近还是不要一个人出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 辛苦你特地跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺诺 宁宁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没能救下她们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从「古物」手中…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 小夜也许办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.62,0:03:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明约好了要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.72,0:03:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和谁约好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.08,0:03:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要保护大家的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲也是 作为这所神社的巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到神谕 讨伐「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也…定下了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能救下眼前的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许能和「古物」战斗的巫女只有你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜 你准备怎么对付「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会打败它们的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在两人决定一同尝试的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要有这样的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 这个实验还需要别的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是为了证明双方观点哪方正确的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有两个人是不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你准备好了吗 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 今天听到的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我听错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.82,0:06:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我很震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还会有能说话的「古物」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对「古物」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是应该打败我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我从你身上感觉不到恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶意不是一直放在外面的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能被高明地藏匿起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.34,0:06:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指的是「古物」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除「古物」之外亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是「古物」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.90,0:07:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我能感到强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.58,0:07:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿望?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有人为了实现愿望而来到店里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.57,0:07:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店里?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 店里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么店?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以实现愿望的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那家店的看门狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是老板
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人都是狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确有狗来过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 来客各种都有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为能实现愿望的店的老板的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有人许下愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那个与我有关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.59,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么是怎样的愿望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个现在也不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你确定没弄错么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直住在这个镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没出去过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不认识你店里的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.49,0:08:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.63,0:08:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我说 约定好了要保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确约好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒「古物」 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不起和谁约定了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望是需要代价的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.17,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 代价必须与愿望相等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以做的很有限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以这个样子出现 便是限制之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我约好了会实现这个愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且一定会做到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.71,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前 我会在小夜身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.73,0:09:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.22,0:10:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间还早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法镇静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在想「这时候 古物不知什么时候会出现」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.41,0:10:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它带去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅如此 让它一直在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 小夜?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 难过的时候不要强颜欢笑哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天没吃晚饭就睡了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳先生告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在做意式调味饭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先吃这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前文人先生说过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guimauve的触感和某个东西很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘴唇…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.35,0:12:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有意式调味饭不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎鸡蛋和热沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.64,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸色似乎好些了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.27,0:12:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为吃过文人先生美味的早餐还有咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 便当和Guimauve
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.62,0:12:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午茶的时候吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间还很充裕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为可以在街上慢慢转转的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天停课
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没通知你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 今天出来得很早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时可能要一直停课了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为还没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 即便是找到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕也会很糟糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前跟你说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.23,0:14:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃人的东西的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求卫诺诺和宁宁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.89,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定已经被那个东西给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直失踪到现在的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计也一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 你也这么想吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 头又痛了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就回去吧 回到你父亲那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒鸟老师为什么突然说那些话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于「古物」似乎知道些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.38,0:15:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去学校?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天应该停课的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 通知来之前就从家里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.17,0:15:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶快回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.12,0:15:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在虽说还很早 可要是发生什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真窝囊 居然变得如此地弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被打败的家伙一样窝囊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的你暂且不论
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被这种水准的人消灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算活了下来 也只有耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有和你打呢 凭什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱 太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我母亲战斗过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这把神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和母亲相比 我或许弱了些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我一定要把你们「古物」打败
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的父亲 唯芳是这么说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个神社里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆着一幅玄乎的脸 给你一把神刀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太可笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑毛!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能忍住笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯芳居然让你来打败我们?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和唯芳都太蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这不正是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲才不愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他坚强而又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从母亲去世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一直在支持着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在讲什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你 你究竟在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是想迷惑我的鬼话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡言乱语的是人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用胡言乱语和谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断地违反着约定的 是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趁早给我消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 把唯芳也灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.71,0:20:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 能和思慕的父亲一同被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.95,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是你的心愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让你到父亲那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就是这感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好去问问唯芳 你的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时真…同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和谁约定要打倒古物的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要实现愿望的 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牵扯进来的话会很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就更想知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.80,0:23:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.88,0:23:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你对于我是很特别的 小夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 Blood-C
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.06,0:23:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人生在世







